WEBVTT

00:00.027 --> 00:03.337
<i>Previously on AMC's
</i>"TURN: Washington's Spies"...

00:03.352 --> 00:05.073
We Tories have to stick together.

00:05.073 --> 00:07.033
She has a husband in the British army.

00:07.033 --> 00:09.033
We need to know who else
she's working with.

00:09.605 --> 00:11.605
You have more friends
in the city than you may know.

00:11.838 --> 00:13.809
Simcoe knows you're Culper.

00:13.810 --> 00:16.003
His father was killed by rebels.
He joined up for revenge.

00:16.003 --> 00:17.598
- What was his name?
- Woodhull.

00:17.598 --> 00:20.497
It will be on the field that we
truly settle our account.

00:20.498 --> 00:23.273
He thanked me for giving up my friend!

00:23.444 --> 00:26.435
We've received emergency orders
to leave for Virginia tonight.

00:26.435 --> 00:27.467
Virginia?

00:27.468 --> 00:29.729
Finally we'll meet
the bloody rebels in combat.

